            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In honorem <lb n="2"/>domus <expan><abbr>divin</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>ex decreto ordinis <lb n="4"/>saltus Sumelocennen<lb break="no" n="5"/>sis curam <expan><abbr>agentib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> Dextro et <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Turran</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>Marciano i<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ter(um)</supplied> <expan><abbr>mag</abbr><ex>istris</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inschriftfeld in Form einer tabula ansata; in der rechten ansa eine Mondsichel. Z. 7: Lücke nach Marciano, evtl. &amp;quot;&amp;quot;vici&amp;quot;&amp;quot;. Autopsie R. Wiegels. (B): Filtzinger; Gaubartz-Sattler; Luik - Reutti: Z. 7: [vici?] mag(istris); Haug - Sixt: Z. 7: Marciano [---].</p>
            </div>
